author: Minyvonne Burke
title: Queen Elizabeth II turns 94 on Tuesday, but birthday gun salute is canceled
description: Queen Elizabeth II turns 94 on Tuesday, but a traditional gun salute to honor her birthday has been canceled due to the pandemic and lockdown orders in the United Kingdom.
content:
A traditional gun salute to honor the birthday of Queen's Elizabeth II birthday will not take place this year due to the coronavirus pandemic and lockdown orders in the United Kingdom.
